name: Searchkick
overview:
Searchkick apps bring your interest and membership data right into your search results. E.g. if you are enroll into any frequent flyer program then you can instantly discover if any retail business gives you miles for shopping there.

Searchkick goes beyond just earning miles and saving money. It also helps you to be in touch with your interests. E.g. if you are a developer then instantly discovering which services have their API is quick way to spark your creativity.

Searchkicks:

Searchkick beta is launched with following searchkicks ready to use in categories like: Miles, Technology, TV, Credit Cards, Social etc.

       AAdvantage
       USAirways
       CrunchBase
       ProgrammableWeb
       XfinityTV
       AmericanExpress
       DiscoverCard
       Twitter

New searchkicks are getting added everyday and you can add/remove searchkicks based on what you want.

Explore all searchkicks here: http://mysearchkick.com/searchkicks.aspx?skCatId=All

Create Your Own Searchkicks:

Searchkick provides a very unique and easy to use service to individuals for recommending products and services to their friends & to businesses to reach out to their audience with real-time promotions and discounts.

Learn more in details on how you can create your own searchkicks. http://mysearchkick.com/guide.aspx
